        <mxCell id="200" value="DCMS&#xa;Debt Collection Management System&#xa;&#xa;Manages the full lifecycle of DWP debt - from referral through recovery, enforcement, and write-off.&#xa;&#xa;Spring Boot 3.4 | React | PostgreSQL 16 | Flowable | Keycloak 24" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dbe8ff;strokeColor=#4f7ccf;fontColor=#0b2e6d;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1;arcSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
